Directors of Bergen Bank, den Norske Credit Bank, two of Norway leading bank, na dem come yarn sey dem don gree to di formal merger of di bank.

Di merger go create di seventh largest bank wey get 210 billion kroner (wey be sey na 30.3 billion).

Banks talk sey one application wey dem dey drag togeder with one entity wey dem dey call Den Norske Bank AS dem send am Monday go Finance Ministry.

Di two board yarn for inside joint statement say di proposed merger agreement, dem consider am for separate board meeting for Oslo Monday.

De say di agreement go dey submitted to deir respective supervisor next Wednesday.

Extraordinary General Meeting, wey be Nov. 28 go determine di share exchange rate.

Sey di merger, na Norwegian goment go do am.

